nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE ACCELERATES EAST-NORTHEASTWARD, STILL A TROPICAL STORM...
summary: ...OCTAVE ACCELERATES EAST-NORTHEASTWARD, STILL A TROPICAL STORM... As of 8:00 PM MST Wed Oct 08 the center of Octave was located near 16.1, -113.2 with movement ENE at 17 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1001 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
